A car is a popular means of transportation.
It has four wheels and an engine.
Cars help people travel quickly from one place to another.
They come in different colors, sizes, and models.
Some cars use petrol or diesel, while others run on electricity.
Cars have seats, doors, windows, and a steering wheel.
Seat belts help keep passengers safe.
Regular maintenance keeps a car in good condition.
Traffic rules should always be followed while driving.
